Here at Intel we create world changing technology that enriches the lives of every person on earth. We are inspired to drive innovation that makes the world safer, builds healthy and vibrant communities and reaches around the globe to better society business and the planet. Our engineers are passionate about finding meaningful solutions for our customers greatest challenges and are united in our purpose to deliver on bold goals. The Data Platforms Group is looking for a passionate data scientist to join our Platform Validation Data Science team. 
In this role you will: 
Work on challenging projects that vary from data analysis and machine learning to automation and platform design 
Gain exposure to how data science is used in real world problems and solutions while applying your knowledge to leading edge industry technology solutions 
Gain insights into project planning activities, team collaboration and cross team organizations 
Be a member of a team who will collaborate with others to deliver high quality results on time 
Use your communication skills as needed for team collaboration and showcase your strong quantitative analytical problem-solving skills 
